info.name: Tumblr - Minimalist Theme
info.description:
A grey-based minimalistic dashboard theme for Tumblr.
No curved edges. No box shadows. Just flat and minimal.

My blog: http://stinking.tumblr.com
info.additionalInfo:
Something wrong with this theme? Check if it's fully up to date and if the problem persists, please ask a question at the bottom of the page!
